    "description": "The FlagStone Core is a multi-chip embedded cryptographic module used within the Eclypt ranges of drives. The FlagStone Core, and subsequently the Eclypt ranges of drives utilising the FlagStone Core, provide access control and data encryption services to protect access to data stored on a connected HDD/SSD (Hard Disk Drive/Solid Data Drive). All accessible sectors on a drive connected to a FlagStone Core are encrypted. The Eclypt range of drives includes Eclypt, Eclypt Freedom and Eclypt Nano.",
